title: Retrieve your won items
description: Retrieves a list of purchases for the authenticated user. Multiple-quantity auctions can be purchased multiple times.
permission_required: MyTradeMeRead: Read your membership & listing data.

path.name: filter
path.description: A filter on the results. AllReturn all won items in the last 45 days.Last30DaysReturns items won in the last 30 days.Last7DaysReturns items won in the last 7 days.Last24HoursReturns items won in the last 24 hours.

enum.name: xml
enum.description: Serialize responses into XML.

enum.name: json
enum.description: Serialize responses into JSON.

query.name: page
query.description: The page number of the set of results to return, starting from 1. Defaults to 1.

query.name: photo_size
query.description: The size of the images to return in the results. Defaults to Thumbnail.

query.name: rows
query.description: The number of results per page; also the maximum number of results to return. Defaults to 50.

returns.description: <WonItems> A list of items the authenticated user has purchased.

fields.name: TotalCount
fields.description: The total number of results in the collection. Can be larger than the number of returned results.

fields.name: Page
fields.description: The index of the current page of results (starts at 1).

fields.name: PageSize
fields.description: The number of results in the current page.

fields.name: List
fields.description: A list of the results in the current page.

fields.name: ListingId
fields.type:
ListingId 
 Integer 

The ID of the listing.



 Title 
 String or null 

The listing title.



 Category 
 String or null 

The listing category.



 StartPrice 
 Number 

The start price.



 StartDate 
 DateTime 

The date the listing was created.



 EndDate 
 DateTime 

The date the listing will end.



 AsAt 
 DateTime 

The date and time the response was generated on the server.



 CategoryPath 
 String or null 

The category path.



 PictureHref 
 String or null 

The URL of the primary photo for the listing (if the listing has a photo). By default you'll get a thumbnail-sized photo, but you can control the size of the photo using the photo_size parameter.



 PhotoId 
 Integer 

The ID of the primary photo for the listing (if the listing has a photo).



 Seller 
 <Member> or null 

The seller of the item.






 MemberId 
 Integer 

The ID of the member. This may be 0, if we determine it is necessary to protect the member's privacy.



 Nickname 
 String or null 

The nickname of the member. Some characters may be changed, if we determine it is necessary to protect the member's privacy.



 DateAddressVerified 
 DateTime 

The date the member was address verified.



 DateJoined 
 DateTime 

The date the member joined.



 Email 
 String or null 

The member's email address.



 UniqueNegative 
 Integer 

The number of distinct members who have placed negative feedback against this member.



 UniquePositive 
 Integer 

The number of distinct members who have placed positive feedback against this member.



 FeedbackCount 
 Integer 

The member's total feedback (UniquePositive minus UniqueNegative).



 IsAddressVerified 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the member has been address verified.



 IsDealer 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the member is a car dealer.






 HasPayNow 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the item has Pay Now.



 IsNew 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the item is marked as new.



 BidCount 
 Integer 

The number of bids on the item.



 IsReserveMet 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the item's reserve has been met.



 HasReserve 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the item has a reserve.



 HasBuyNow 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the item has Buy Now.



 Note 
 String or null 

The note on an item.



 NoteId 
 Integer 

The note id on an item.



 NoteDate 
 DateTime 

The date of the note on an item.



 CategoryName 
 String or null 

The display name of the category.



 ReserveState 
 Enumeration 

The flag to display on an item.



 IsClassified 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the item is a classified.



 RelistedItemId 
 Integer 

The ID of the new listing if this listing was relisted.



 Subtitle 
 String or null 

The subtitle, if present.



 IsBuyNowOnly 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether or not this is a Buy Now Only listing.



 Quantity 
 Integer 

The total quantity available of the item. Only applicable for Buy Now Only listings. When retrieving won items this value represents the number sold, not the total quantity. When retrieving sold items, this value is not present (use QuantitySold instead). When retrieving listing details, this value is only present if you are the seller.



 IsFlatShippingCharge 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether one flat shipping fee will be charged if more than one of this item is purchased. Only applicable for Buy Now Only listings.



 RemainingGalleryPlusRelists 
 Integer or null 

The number of times the item can be relisted and get the gallery promotion for free. This value is only present if you are the seller and the listing had the gallery promotion applied due to the gallery plus promotion. Note that for this field, a value of zero is not the same as if the field is missing (a value of zero means gallery plus is in effect whereas if the field is missing it means that you are not the seller or gallery plus is not in effect).



 IsClearance 
 Boolean 

This indicates that the listing is a clearance item. Clearance listings include listings with was/now pricing and general clearance stock.



 WasPrice 
 Number or null 

The usual price that a product is sold at, or the price before it was marked down. This is always more than the Buy Now price for Auctions, or more than the asking price for Classifieds.This field will only be populated if IsClearance is true.



 PercentageOff 
 Integer or null 

The percentage that a product has been discounted. This has been rounded for display purposes. This field will only be populated if IsClearance is true.



 Options 
 Collection of <Option> or null 

The combination of variant options that this variant represents.




                                 (This type has already been defined)
                        


 ListingGroupId 
 Integer or null 

The identifier of the group of related multi-variant listings. Blank if the listing is not multi-variant



 HasPing 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether Ping is a supported payment option.



 StatusDate 
 DateTime 

The date the status was last changed.



 AuctionAttribute 
 String or null 

The auction attributes.



 BuyerFeedbackPlaced 
 Integer 

Indicates whether feedback has been placed by the buyer (0 = no, 1 = yes).



 SellerFeedbackPlaced 
 Integer 

Indicates whether feedback has been placed by the seller (0 = no, 1 = yes).



 DeliveryId 
 Integer 

The ID of the delivery information (address, phone number, etc).



 FpoDecisionViaMobile 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the fixed price offer came from a mobile phone.



 HasPaidByCreditCard 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the payment was made with a credit card using Pay Now.



 InvoiceId 
 Integer 

The ID of the invoice associated with the purchase.



 OfferId 
 Integer 

The ID of the fixed price offer (if one was made).



 PaymentInfo 
 String or null 

A comma-separated list of the available payment options e.g. "NZ Bank Deposit, Cash, Pay Now".



 Price 
 Number 

The price the item was sold for, excluding shipping. If the purchase was for multiple items, this is the price of a single item.



 SelectedShipping 
 String or null 

A description of the selected shipping method (e.g. "Nationwide courier").



 ShippingPrice 
 Number 

The price of the selected shipping method. Multi-quantity purchases are not accounted for (use TotalShippingPrice for that).



 ShippingType 
 Enumeration 

The type of shipping that was selected.



 SoldDate 
 DateTime 

The date and time the sale happened.



 SoldType 
 String or null 

The type of sale ("offer", "buynow" or "auction").



 PaymentInstructions 
 String or null 

The payment instructions that the seller has sent to the buyer, containing information on how to pay. Will be empty if the seller has not enabled payment instructions, or if the seller has not yet sent them to the buyer.



 PurchaseId 
 Integer 

A unique ID that identifies the sale.



 ReferenceNumber 
 String or null 

The reference number that should be used when making a deposit into the seller's bank account.



 SubtotalPrice 
 Number 

The price for all items, excluding shipping (i.e. equal to Price * Quantity).



 TotalShippingPrice 
 Number 

The total price for shipping. If flat shipping is not enabled, equal to ShippingPrice * Quantity.



 TotalSalePrice 
 Number 

The total price for the entire sale, including shipping. If the purchase was for multiple items, all items are included in this price.



 CreditCardLastFourDigits 
 String or null 

The last four digits of the credit card used to pay for the item. Only available if Pay Now was used to make the purchase.



 OrderId 
 Integer or null 

If the item was purchased via the shopping cart then a purchased cart id is returned which is called order Id.



 TrackedParcels 
 Collection of <TrackedParcel> or null 

Tracked courier parcels for this purchase






 CourierParcelId 
 Integer 

The ID of this parcel



 CourierCompanyName 
 String or null 

The name of the courier company



 TrackingReference 
 String or null 

The tracking reference



 TrackingUrl 
 String or null 

The tracking url



 Status 
 Enumeration or null 

Last event of this parcel



 DateAdded 
 DateTime or null 

Date the tracking parcel order was created






 TaxSubTotal 
 Number 

Sum of all taxes included in this purchase



 HasPaidByDeferredPayment 
 Boolean 

Indicates whether the payment was made with afterpay.

enum.name: None
enum.description: There is no reserve on the item (i.e. the reserve price is the same as the starting price).

enum.name: Met
enum.description: The value of the highest bid has exceeded the reserve price.

enum.name: NotMet
enum.description: The value of the highest bid has not reached the reserve price.

enum.name: NotApplicable
enum.description: The listing cannot have a reserve because bidding is not allowed. This may be because it is a classified or because it is a Buy Now Only auction.

enum.name: None
enum.description: The type of the "None of the options apply to me" shipping option. Do not use when listing an item.

enum.name: Unknown
enum.description: Obsolete. Do not use.

enum.name: Undecided
enum.description: Indicates that the seller will confirm the shipping details with the buyer directly. This shipping option cannot be used when Pay Now is specified as a payment option. When listing an item, this option cannot be used in combination with other shipping options.

enum.name: Pickup
enum.description: Indicates the item can be picked up. Do not use when listing an item (use thePickupfield instead).

enum.name: Free
enum.description: Indicates the item can be shipped for free within New Zealand. When listing an item, this option cannot be used in combination with other shipping options.

enum.name: Custom
enum.description: Custom shipping option. Allows the seller to specify the price and description. Multiple custom shipping options are allowed (up to ten).

enum.name: TradeMe
enum.description: Trademe shipping option. Allows the seller to calculate the quotes from couriers, all calculated quotes will be saved in custom shipping options.
